If it seems like you've seen this topic before, you have. This is my second topic for this. Didn't want to gravedig my old one, because I am just now restarting Runescape again.
Alright, after many tries, I have realized that all public parties for Dungeoneering are far from competent.
I'd like a few people to make one with me (preferably 4 other people) that can constantly no-life this skill with me.
My stats: CB: 89 Att: 73 Str: 73 Def: 70 Hp: 75 Prayer: 47 Range: 73 Mage: 80 [b]Dungeoneering[/b]: 58 [size=8pt]Note: I will try to keep this up to date with my current stats.[/size]
I would like to do all floors with this party. Meaning, together we would do the max we could. If we're not going to your full potential for prestige, we can do the same Dungeon a few times to get your higher same-type floors ticked.
Preferably, have a Dungeoneering level around 50-65 (I will be accepting >40, in some circumstances).
Schedule:
[ul][li]F1-F19 = C1 Rush, Small, 5:1 Difficulty[/li] [li]F20-F24 = C6, Small, 5:1 Difficulty[/li] [li]F25-F29 = C6, Med, 5:5 Difficulty[/li] [li]F30-F__ = C6, Large, 5:5 Difficulty[/li][/ul]
I will by default be the keyer. If you think you have the potential to be better, I'll give you a few floors to test you on and, if you are better, you will be the new keyer.
P.S. I'm not a dumbass, and I know what I'm doing when I'm dungeoneering.
Please post any 'applications' in the following form: [code] CB: Hp: Attack: Strength: Defence: Ranged: Prayer: Magic: Dungeoneering: Any side notes (F2P/P2P): [/code]
If you're accepted, PM me your rsn.
Current party (mopar user : rsn): eyeownyew : 6e9 RiiPiiNFtW : RiiPiiNFtW Speljohan : tinyscape : foz [J]ava : Rub My Ox Travas : Battla Masta mihalich : N S X
Ex-members (just tell me if you wish to rejoin): casey Pure2ownage Fuscate Cerebro Kieron97 Davidi2 LilxCJ Wyrmcabbage rip4d xxlukexx
